          </li>
          <li id="2x">
            <p>Previewing Markdown</p>
            <ul>
              <li id="VS4">
                <p>Marked</p>
                <ul>
                  <li id="Uqw">
                    <p>You can preview and print from Markdown texts and clipboards, applying different CSS stylesheets, with [Marked 2](https://marked2app.com/).</p>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </li>
